				To obtain a photo copy of a genealogical record or an obituary   from the La Porte Herald-Argus (or one of its predecessors), send your <a href="http://docs.google.com/viewer?url=http://www.laportelibrary.org/genealogy/genreqform.pdf" target="_blank" class="ugdv_link">genealogy request form</a> to the address below.
