			<p>
				Requests must include the following:
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li style="padding-left: 3px;">
					Your written request for information with as much specific information as possible.
				</li>
				<li style="padding-left: 3px;">
					A check or money order to cover the cost of your request (no   cash, please).  Make checks/money orders out to La Porte County Public   Library.
				</li>
				<li style="padding-left: 3px;">
					$5.00 for the initial search requested (person, record, event, subject, etc.)
				</li>
				<li style="padding-left: 3px;">
					$1.00 for each additional search requested, up to four (4).
				</li>
				<li style="padding-left: 3px;">
					A self-addressed stamped envelope.
				</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Example: A search for an obituary for Mary Smith will cost $5.00. A   search for an obituary for Mary Smith and a search for John Smith's   obituary will cost $6.00. Searches for five (5) different records, the   maximum per written request, will cost $9.00.
			</p>
			<p>
				You will receive one photocopy of our findings for each of your   requested searches.  You may ask for a maximum of FIVE (5) searches per   written request.  Refunds will be made for unsuccessful searches.
